query:
SELECT sr.id, sr.siteId, s.siteNumber, sr.name, sr.startDate, sr.endDate, 
sr.weekdayRate, sr.weekendRate, sr.weeklyRate,
s.pricePerDay as baseWeekdayRate, s.weekendPricePerDay as baseWeekendRate
FROM seasonalRates sr 
JOIN sites s ON sr.siteId = s.id 
JOIN shopping_centres c ON s.centreId = c.id 
WHERE c.name LIKE '%Chullora%' 
AND sr.startDate <= '2026-06-14' 
AND sr.endDate >= '2026-06-13'
LIMIT 5;
